Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.28,0:01:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.57,0:01:44.25,Title2,,0,0,0,,{\fs42\fad(450,400)\blur6\pos(1021,168)}就像融化一般
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.42,0:01:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請問一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.92,0:01:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}呃... 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.59,0:02:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請給我一個最甜的麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.22,0:02:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}呃... 歡迎光臨...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.51,0:02:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要甜的麵包是嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.10,0:02:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}恩 請給我一個甜的像要融化一樣的麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.48,0:02:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 對不起 馬上就要到停業時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.02,0:02:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}甜的麵包基本都賣光了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.53,0:02:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼！...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.70,0:02:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是開玩笑的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.03,0:02:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊... 巧克力丹麥酥的話還剩一個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.29,0:02:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那麼請給我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.30,0:02:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}昨天來買甜麵包的客人 今天已經幫他準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.22,0:02:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不知道他還會再過來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.35,0:02:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}晚上吃甜麵包 真稀奇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.43,0:02:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可能是個愛睡懶覺的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.02,0:02:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.39,0:02:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.69,0:02:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天也是甜麵包 請給我三個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.82,0:02:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好的~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.78,0:03:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}您選哪個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.03,0:03:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.70,0:03:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊... 這個... 跟這個...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.41,0:03:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}感謝惠顧~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.59,0:03:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天要這個哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.76,0:03:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那麼就要這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.76,0:03:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就選這個麵包吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.47,0:03:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}感謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.85,0:03:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的每天都來買呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.31,0:03:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看來對我們的麵包很滿意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.90,0:03:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.36,0:03:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}每天都來買甜麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.16,0:03:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}讓那位使魔前來購買
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.03,0:03:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那不是一位很好的客人嗎~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.24,0:03:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然是這樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.04,0:03:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}每次選麵包的時候就會不斷的深思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.54,0:03:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好像有什麼緣由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.00,0:04:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}恩 這樣的話 下次嘗試送點麵包過去給她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.01,0:04:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}趁這個機會 我也試著考慮一下新菜單
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.89,0:04:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這幾個...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.50,0:04:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們這樣好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為就算我們說了 要幫他送過去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.92,0:04:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他也不會聽進去的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.75,0:04:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好了 好了~  夠了吧~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.94,0:05:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.19,0:05:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.15,0:05:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要迷路了...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.45,0:05:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等一下 不要說嚇人的話啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.50,0:05:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要進去嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.46,0:05:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這種地方原來還有房子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.05,0:05:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.30,0:05:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}索魯貝 不要買這種的 要說幾次你才會懂啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是... 梅露蒂大小姐...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.06,0:05:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊！~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.65,0:05:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.73,0:05:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.19,0:05:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒...　沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.78,0:05:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哦呀！ 你們是麵包店的...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.19,0:05:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼你們會在這裡呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.74,0:05:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那是...因為...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.37,0:05:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個... 本店推出了新口味
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.99,0:05:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想盡快通知喜歡麵包的顧客
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.00,0:05:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是這樣啊~ 那真是有勞你們了~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.04,0:06:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是索魯貝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.84,0:06:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是這間別館主人的使魔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊... 我是亞蜜露
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.30,0:06:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是妮莉絲和艾雅莉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.30,0:06:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一直提供美味的麵包 真是太感謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.47,0:06:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請務必和我主人見一面~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.48,0:06:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗎~？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.27,0:06:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好的~ 請務必~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這邊請~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.86,0:06:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來 來~ 這邊走~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.78,0:06:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.78,0:06:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好厲害！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.58,0:06:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好華麗...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.62,0:06:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}豪華~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.67,0:06:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是好冷！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.75,0:06:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.67,0:06:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}總覺得好甜的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.80,0:06:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是真的啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是和麵包的香味有點差別
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.89,0:06:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}索魯貝 他們幾個是誰啊！？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.39,0:06:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大... 大小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.86,0:07:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是馬黛拉麵包店的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.74,0:07:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是來送新菜單的麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.96,0:07:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我的主人梅露蒂大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.96,0:07:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為了開發出究極的甜點每天都在進行研究
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.38,0:07:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊~ 所以剛剛才會一直聞到甜味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.76,0:07:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖是這麼說 但是一直沒辦法做出想要味道...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要多嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.89,0:07:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.31,0:07:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.19,0:07:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哼~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.11,0:07:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個麵包店的呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.28,0:07:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我覺得能成為究極甜點的參考 所以前來購買你們的麵包進行研究
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.08,0:07:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}原來是這樣的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.49,0:08:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是我們的味道好像滿足不了你們的需求...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.87,0:08:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.29,0:08:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.75,0:08:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個... 這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.29,0:08:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.17,0:08:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想做的究極甜點是冰淇淋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.88,0:08:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對啦 是這樣不行嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.76,0:08:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不~ 只是覺得做好冰淇淋好像很困難的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.43,0:08:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}甜味的掌握真的很複雜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.85,0:08:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}口感的變化也是永無止境呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.69,0:08:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是... 是阿！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.52,0:08:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想嘗試著添加新味道 但是味道馬上就會混雜在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.99,0:08:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}口感也會不同
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.82,0:08:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還有溫度跟攪拌的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.41,0:08:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要求真是太纖細了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.49,0:08:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}呃...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.74,0:08:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這種事跟你們也沒有關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.54,0:08:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}話說回來 冰淇淋是冰冷的食品
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.04,0:08:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}熱乎乎的麵包怎麼可能做為參考呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.79,0:08:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大... 大小姐...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嘛 不要這麼說呀 難得都送過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.34,0:08:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來嘗看看吧~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.76,0:09:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哇 跟以往一樣的美味呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.43,0:09:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哼 普通啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.93,0:09:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也可以嘗一嘗嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.60,0:09:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 請享用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.86,0:09:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哇 這... 這個真是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.65,0:09:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}清爽的酸甜中散發出極致的香甜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.28,0:09:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請大小姐也務必品嚐一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.03,0:09:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}其他的麵包也請...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.75,0:09:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.67,0:09:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想吃的時後就吃吧~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.46,0:09:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那麼 不好意思了 真是太感謝了...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.63,0:09:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}回去...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.71,0:09:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦！？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.72,0:09:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}總之快點回去啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.59,0:09:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對你們真是不好意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.10,0:09:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒關係 不用太在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.02,0:09:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}下次請梅露蒂來店裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.44,0:09:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}自己親手挑選麵包這樣可能會比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.15,0:09:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.15,0:09:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是大小姐極討厭踏出別館外...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.11,0:09:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}索魯貝 你在幹嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.70,0:09:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好 馬上就來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.20,0:10:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那麼我先失陪了 今天真是太感謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.79,0:10:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}究極的冰淇淋嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.04,0:10:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能完成就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.96,0:10:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為了梅露蒂 有什麼能幫上忙的就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.51,0:10:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哈...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.93,0:10:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.23,0:10:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然很不甘心 但是她們的麵包真的很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.60,0:10:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要是能做出像這麵包一樣甜到快融化的冰淇淋就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.11,0:10:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大小姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.78,0:10:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那麼就讓我們去找出這麼好吃的秘訣吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.74,0:10:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.96,0:10:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這邊請~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.13,0:10:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這麼早的時間出門 真讓人不敢相信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.34,0:11:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別這麼說嘛~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.59,0:11:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在下我也是非常期待著啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.14,0:11:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以我才這麼討厭出門啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.18,0:11:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊！~ 沒受傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.35,0:11:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來 讓我扶您
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.82,0:11:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我一個人也能站起來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.78,0:11:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.70,0:11:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好的 大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.93,0:11:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}奶油麵包 烤好了哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.93,0:11:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}歡迎光臨~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.35,0:11:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}感謝惠顧~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.90,0:12:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我家的老頭子 最近牙齒不太好 咬不動太硬的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.36,0:12:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那樣的話 可以嘗試看看蒸蛋麵包哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.20,0:12:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}薄薄的外層裡面也是非常鬆軟的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.99,0:12:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}唷 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.16,0:12:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊~ 歡迎光臨！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.66,0:12:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}做好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.46,0:12:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}洋蔥萵苣黃瓜沙拉和滿滿的牛肉片所做的特別麵包籃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.67,0:12:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}唔呼呼呼~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.34,0:12:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看上去很好吃的樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.88,0:12:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}感謝啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}吃完後的感想記得告訴我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.84,0:12:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嘿唷！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.26,0:12:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.93,0:12:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}路上小心~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.82,0:12:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天也有當個乖孩子嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.69,0:12:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來~ 按順序來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.28,0:12:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家都有的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.70,0:12:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來~ 小熊麵包！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.99,0:12:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝 艾雅莉姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.20,0:12:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哥哥 好狡猾 我也想要小熊麵包呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.62,0:12:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你吃不下這麼大的麵包吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.25,0:12:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是我就是想要啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.50,0:12:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒關係的~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.59,0:12:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.09,0:12:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.50,0:13:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哇~  謝謝！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.63,0:13:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.26,0:13:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不管在哪都很有人氣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.47,0:13:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}前段時間的山梅羊角麵包 我的家人也非常喜歡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.93,0:13:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是這樣啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.93,0:13:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}承蒙你的照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.48,0:13:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}阿啦~ 這個看起也滿好吃的樣子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.40,0:13:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}季節到來的話 杏仁口味的甜麵包也會有的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.86,0:13:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「羊角麵包真好吃」被這麼表揚了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.66,0:13:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}用當季的食材來製作 果然都能被接受呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.12,0:13:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}客人對我們這麼說的話 是最好不過的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.12,0:13:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}特製的牛肉麵包籃也很美味
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.87,0:13:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那樣的大小 份量足夠嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.04,0:13:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在多圍一圈的話 也是能做出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}下次我問看看呢~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.42,0:13:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}蒸麵包類的要不要增加在菜單上啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.22,0:13:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.22,0:13:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有位顧客想吃鬆軟的麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.64,0:13:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大... 大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.56,0:13:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要回去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.65,0:14:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天想給輝夜送了丹麥吉士麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.15,0:14:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼樣呢 吃了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.15,0:14:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過... 他還在睡著
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.74,0:14:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}睡了的話 我們也無法得知好不好吃了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.08,0:14:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以我考慮了下 做香味十足的麵包怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.79,0:14:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊~ 這真是個好主意~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.25,0:14:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}順利的話或許也能告訴梅露蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.71,0:14:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}梅露蒂？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.92,0:14:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊~ 就是那位喜歡購買甜麵包的顧客
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.30,0:14:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}說著準備做出究極冰淇淋的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.97,0:14:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然住在小鎮外面的屋子裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.51,0:14:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是房子非常的不得了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.52,0:14:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}製作冰淇淋的道具還有素材什麼的 有一大堆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}展現出想認真製作出美味冰淇淋的這種感覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.27,0:14:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.61,0:14:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真想見一面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.78,0:14:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是好像不太喜歡外出的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.82,0:14:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那麼就做出梅露蒂想親自外出 而購買的美味麵包吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.17,0:15:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不好意思！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.59,0:15:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來了~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.55,0:15:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.55,0:15:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這可真是~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.80,0:15:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}晚安 這麼晚了來拜訪真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.06,0:15:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不不 今次來訪有什麼事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.81,0:15:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來送麵包給梅露蒂了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.31,0:15:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然知道會給你們添麻煩...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.23,0:15:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}試著做了 能成為究極冰淇淋的參考麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.32,0:15:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家 為了大小姐...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.49,0:15:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}感激不盡...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.12,0:15:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然很想讓大小姐親自來感謝...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.87,0:15:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊... 沒關係的 我們幾個擅自製作的而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.58,0:15:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那麼告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.37,0:15:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.25,0:15:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.55,0:15:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}讓她們進來也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.21,0:15:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大小姐...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.88,0:15:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那麼為了大家開設甜點饗宴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.78,0:16:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不好意思讓你們久等了~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.75,0:16:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那麼就有勞大家開始宴會了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.21,0:16:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我做了 蜂蜜香草吐司
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.38,0:16:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}淋上濃濃的蜂蜜和焦糖香草的清淡甜味哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.30,0:16:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我找到剩餘的材料 做出了丹麥藍莓麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.39,0:16:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我覺得稍微有點酸味的話 可能會比較可口一點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.85,0:16:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我的話是奶皇派！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.90,0:16:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為收到了新鮮的雞蛋 於是...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.15,0:16:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哇~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.57,0:16:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.94,0:16:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不管哪個都很合大小姐的口味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.41,0:16:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不吃一下的話是不知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.49,0:17:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咿~ 肯定會很美味的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.41,0:17:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請吧 從喜歡的開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.43,0:17:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大小姐 覺得怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.27,0:17:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}美味...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.23,0:17:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.77,0:17:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}美味 全部都 太好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.81,0:17:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}比之前所吃過的麵包都要美味
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.36,0:17:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.57,0:17:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}剛開始還覺得不行了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.53,0:17:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝~ 梅露蒂~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.66,0:17:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大小姐 等...這裡怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.91,0:17:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大...大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.38,0:17:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等一下...大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.34,0:18:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大小姐 到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.01,0:18:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒事 別管我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.56,0:18:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}索魯貝去繼續宴會
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.14,0:18:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大... 大小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.63,0:18:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.44,0:18:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哇~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.56,0:18:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看起來好美味的樣子~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.02,0:18:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 非常的~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.98,0:18:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}快點開始吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.40,0:18:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}都快融化了不是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.78,0:18:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.03,0:19:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好吃~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.20,0:19:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}非常得甜美啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.66,0:19:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也好喜歡這個味道~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.41,0:19:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那肯定會好吃的啦...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.04,0:19:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因... 因為和你們用一樣的方法做的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.46,0:19:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.29,0:19:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}多虧了你們的麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.55,0:19:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}究極冰淇淋才會離的更近一步
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.67,0:19:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}偷窺你們的工作場所價值也體現出來了呢~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.01,0:19:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}笨... 笨蛋 索魯貝 又多嘴了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.27,0:19:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是 就像這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.06,0:19:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為了做出究極冰淇淋所需要的是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.98,0:19:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}肯定是想著某人的表情而做的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.24,0:19:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想著某個人的表情...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.53,0:19:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們製作麵包的時候考慮著對方的需求
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.45,0:19:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是為了某個人才用心製作麵包的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.37,0:19:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是你們為了我所製作的麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.42,0:19:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以比起其他任何的麵包都要好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.51,0:20:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我只是為了自己而製作的冰淇淋...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.93,0:20:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想不應該是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.72,0:20:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哈~
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.39,0:20:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大... 大小姐 太好了 真是太好了...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.19,0:20:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.65,0:20:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}阿？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.41,0:20:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.66,0:20:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}索魯貝的份
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.54,0:20:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我的...？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.04,0:20:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}應該是最好吃的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.08,0:20:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想著你的臉而做出來的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.71,0:20:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.89,0:20:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好吃 真的非常好...吃...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.07,0:21:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還想吃的話就說出來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.45,0:21:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好的...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.16,0:21:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是明明還想再吃 但是已經吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.37,0:21:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好了啦~ 來~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.21,0:21:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好... 好的...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.89,0:21:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.02,0:21:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們回來了~ 里克~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.65,0:21:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}歡迎回來~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.61,0:21:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請... 請給我...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.41,0:21:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請給我能讓我和索魯貝都幸福的麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.12,0:21:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}歡迎~
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.67,0:23:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在馬上就到城堡裡送去麵包什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.30,0:23:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的是... 怎麼常常這麼擅作主張呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.30,0:23:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是 這或許是可以直接能和王子直接對話的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.35,0:23:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an8}為了下次也能做出幸福的麵包~
